    "originContent": "**Q**: So what are the \"Larger Goals\" ?<br/>",
    "translatedContent": "**问**：那么，“更大的目标”有哪些？<br/>"
  },
  {
    "row": 66,
    "rowsha": "Q9lFtwgDt33lQK007utRXZDB6l0nAJ7jImygBmmpTZE=",
    "originContent": "**A**: See the __Roadmap__ below for a complete breakdown.",
    "translatedContent": "**答**：请看下面的 __路线图__ 完整细分。"
  },
  {
